                    "text": {
                      "value": "<b>The Under The Pole expeditions explore the “twilight zone” at ocean depths of between 60 and 150 metres and contribute to the major scientific discoveries that will determine the future of our planet.\n</b><br/><br/>\nby Françoise Blind Kempinski"
                    },
                    "videoPoster": {
                      "value": "/data/media/img/les-echos/rolex_org_les_echos_poster_frame.jpg"
                    },
                    "logoAlt": {
